{"tid":2217481,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【港朝換代】林鄭明益中資惹反感 - 大灣區國舅爺","createTime":"2020-09-25T12:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T12:52:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2da39a8ca6cbf642269ce05e3637d400a3de9cf","tid":2217481,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200925/AHQTNQXJYFFYLH4BDDNFI4SBKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200925%2FAHQTNQXJYFFYLH4BDDNFI4SBKE%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=8704c968\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200925%2FAHQTNQXJYFFYLH4BDDNFI4SBKE%2F&h=200604ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200925/AHQTNQXJYFFYLH4BDDNFI4SBKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【港朝換代】林鄭明益中資惹反感 - 大灣區國舅爺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ookHH4ZGOdvqjRz6NkrqgmlORms=/1920x1280/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7UKCLVD3EFAPRLIGWSKK6U2ERE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FookHH4ZGOdvqjRz6NkrqgmlORms%3D%2F1920x1280%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7UKCLVD3EFAPRLIGWSKK6U2ERE.jpg&h=3cb9814b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■兩大連鎖超市品牌惠康和百佳，無緣無故被政府針對，「被推出」折扣優惠，令業界相當不滿。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n兩大連鎖超市品牌惠康和百佳，無緣無故被政府針對，「被推出」折扣優惠。政府選擇性「執法」，摧毀自由市場的價值，難怪無人讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n政權近月再次仗勢凌人，在8月份政府公佈的第二期「保就業」，突然劍指惠康、百佳，要求這兩間超市伸手拿補貼後須向客戶提供折扣，對中資如華潤則刻意縱容，令業界相當不滿。<br />\n<br />\n惠康和百佳的「保就業」計劃第二期申請，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n百佳做法也巧妙，沒有一口氣過把所有細節公佈，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，政府似乎刻意undermine英資，明明人家表明是回饋1.2億元，政府新聞稿卻寫惠康的回饋只有1億元，偷偷計少2,000萬，令人費解。今次政府厚此薄彼，惹來全城反感，只針對惠康和百佳，華潤萬家拿2,155萬、華潤堂拿1,175萬、華潤五豐拿838萬，肆無忌憚地明益中資，打壓英資、港資。<br />\n<br />\n大灣區國舅爺"}]}